    {
      "content": "# Improve the Agent\n\n## Row 0 [~20s]\n**Narrative:** - Path 1: custom code plus custom data\n- Best when tight control matters\n- Shape both logic and grounding directly\n**Actions:** - Show the custom code plus custom data path\n- Point to the relevant code, data, or config artifacts\n- Position this as the high-control option\n**Screenshot:** .cutready/screenshots/20260609_175617_vlcsnap-2026-06-09-17h56m08s196.png\n\n## Row 1 [~20s]\n**Narrative:** - Path 2: your data with Foundry support\n- Use strong domain context already inside the business\n- Improve the agent faster with platform help\n**Actions:** - Show the Foundry-assisted path\n- Focus on enterprise data improving the agent\n- Keep the example tied to the chosen app scenario\n**Screenshot:** .cutready/screenshots/20260609_175442_vlcsnap-2026-06-09-17h54m37s970.png\n\n## Row 2 [~20s]\n**Narrative:** - Path 3: M365 feedback and reinforcement loops\n- Learn from real usage, approvals, and outcomes\n- Improve behavior in the flow of work\n**Actions:** - Show the M365 feedback-driven path\n- Highlight approvals, feedback, or reinforcement signals\n- Keep the emphasis on real usage\n**Screenshot:** .cutready/screenshots/20260609_175643_vlcsnap-2026-06-09-17h56m39s221.png\n\n## Row 3 [~15s]\n**Narrative:** - Summarize the three paths\n- Reinforce that this is now a managed, improvable agent\n- Bridge to fleet visibility and governance\n**Actions:** - Summarize the three paths\n- Reinforce that the agent is now managed and improvable\n- Tee up the governance sketch\n**Design Plan:** Placeholder visual only, per user request. Narrative goal: briefly summarize the three improvement paths and bridge to governance without committing to final design. Hero metaphor: three simple path cards feeding into one managed agent card, with a small governance hint badge. Main objects: 1) title at top saying Working on summary visual, 2) subtitle saying three improvement paths to managed agent, 3) three small cards across the left and center for Code + Data, Foundry Help, and M365 Feedback, 4) one larger managed agent card on the right as the hero destination, 5) a small governance bridge badge beneath or beside the hero card. Layout: centered title and subtitle in the top safe area; three cards arranged left-to-center in a shallow row around y 250; managed agent card on the right around x 690 y 190; governance badge near bottom right of that card. Colors: $background scene, $title and $subtitle for framing text, $surface with $border for cards, $accent for the managed agent emphasis, $secondary and $tertiary as light variety on source cards, $muted for supporting labels. Motion beats: fast fade in title and subtitle, then the three source cards, then arrows or lines to the managed agent card, then governance badge fades in last.\n\n",
      "role": "tool",
      "tool_call_id": "call_GSbLWfcEL5sSBGVeESGNpwJ4"
    },
